                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5839" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0887</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9548 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从事后查错防弊到全面风险防控——步步高内部审计数字赋能之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Engaged in post-error prevention and prevention to comprehensive risk prevention and control——digital empowerment pathway about internal audit in BBG</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钟希余，冯文红，张立，周卓杰，徐攀，袁祥耀，雷蝉羽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湘潭大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">步步高商业连锁股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">监察与纪检部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部审计；数字赋能；风险防控；价值增值</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">internal audit；digital empowerment；risk prevention；value added</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着大数据时代的到来和线上零售行业的蓬勃发展，传统零售企业正逐步向智慧零售迈进，实现线上线下相结合的模式。步步高是湖南的零售龙头企业，在数字化转型的道路上，积极探索内部审计数字化如何赋能公司，其具有代表性。本案例描述了步步高在数字化转型过程中遇到“羊毛党”事件后，内审部门如何对事件进行风险识别、风险评估和风险应对的过程。在对风险事件做到事后查错防弊后，步步高开始思考如何对风险进行提前预警。内审部门利用数字技术，建立了中台数据库，实现各部门间信息流动；搭建了数字化风控预警平台，利用数字资产建立风险模型，对风险进行提前预警，实现数字赋能。在风控预警平台的基础上，步步高提出了围绕价值链进行审计的思路，关联价值链的各个环节，做到全面风险防控，帮助公司实现价值增值。由此引发学术界与企业界对企业内部审计如何利用数字技术赋能企业价值增值的深入探讨。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the advent of the era of big data and the booming online retail industry, traditional retail companies are gradually moving towards smart retail and realizing a combined online and offline model. As a leading retailer in Hunan, BBG is actively exploring how internal audit digitalization can empower the company on the road of digital transformation, which is representative of the company. This case describes how the internal audit department identified, assessed and responded to the &quot;wool party&quot; incident during the digital transformation process. After investigating and preventing errors after the incident, BBG started to think about how to provide early warning of risks. Using digital technology, the internal audit department established a middle desk database to realize the flow of information between departments; it built a digital risk control early warning platform to establish risk models using digital assets to provide early warning of risks and realize digital empowerment. On the basis of the risk control early warning platform, BBG 
proposed the idea of auditing around the value chain, linking various links of the value chain to achieve comprehensive risk prevention and control, and helping the company to realize value-added. This led to an in-depth discussion between the academic and corporate sectors on how to use digital technology to empower value-added enterprises in internal auditing.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》、《大数据与风险管理》、《管理审计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交易费用理论；SWOT模型；内部审计的职能；增值型内部审计理论；传统内审与大数据内审；数字技术相关理论；价值链理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-01</td>
                            </tr>
